g.text: BUSINESS MODELWhat capabilities do this improve? What customer will benefit? How does it change us?
CUSTOMERSHow would our customers be impacted? What are they demanding? How do we know them?
DEVELOPMENT, SUPPORT & COSTWho will build it? Who will support me when something goes wrong?What resources do I need to keep me running time, people, money?
ORGANIZATIONHow does our organization structure support or hinder an agile structure? What would have to change?
METRICS & ANALYTICSHow would we measure this? What support analytics exist?
CULTUREWhat would support this transformation?What would hinder it?
LEADERSHIPHow does our leadership view this change? What do we need to show them to demonstrate a positive direction?
TECHNOLOGYWhat technology do we have in place? What would we need?
ROLLOUT PHASESHow could we demonstrate success quickly? How could we scale that success?
PROCESSHow could we demonstrate success quickly? How could we scale that success?
